ShadowHire Privacy Policy

At ShadowHire, we are committed to safeguarding the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect the information you provide while using our mobile application.

Information We Collect:
To enhance your experience with ShadowHire, we collect the following information:

Name: We collect your name to personalize your interactions with the app.
Email: Your email address is required for communication purposes and to keep you updated about our services.
Phone Number: We request your phone number to facilitate communication and provide timely assistance.
Purpose of Data Collection:
ShadowHire is designed to connect users with private investigators. The information collected is solely used for the following purposes:

User Identification: Your name and email help us identify you uniquely within our system.
Communication: We use your email and phone number to communicate relevant updates and facilitate contact between you and private investigators.
Security Measures:
We employ stringent security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.

Third-Party Disclosure:
ShadowHire does not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your information to outside parties. We prioritize the confidentiality of your data.

By using ShadowHire, you consent to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy. Any changes to this policy will be communicated through the app. For any queries or concerns, please contact us at santosh95.freelance@gmail.com

Thank you for choosing ShadowHire. Your privacy is our priority.
